<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Navbar</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0px;
      }
      body {
      }
      .d1 {
        background-color: black;
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 5px;
        margin-left: 10px;
      }
      ul li a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: rgb(69, 227, 255);
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      ul li {
        margin-top: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        padding-top: 3px;
        padding-left: 13px;
        padding-right: 13px;
        padding-bottom: 3px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border-width: 1px;
        transition: 0.6s all ease-in;
      }
      ul li:hover {
        background-color: rgb(83, 215, 255);
        box-shadow: 3px 4px 9px rgb(120, 197, 248);
      }
      ul li:hover a {
        color: white;
      }
      ul li:active {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        transition: 0.2s all ease-in-out;
      }
      .d2 {
        display: flex;
        background-color: rgb(104, 104, 104);
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        position: relative;
      }
      .d21 {
        display: flex;
        position: absolute;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        animation-name: move;
        animation-duration: 2s;
        animation-iteration-count: 1;
        animation-delay: 1s;
        animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
        left: 30px;
        background-color: whitesmoke;
        border: 2px solid bisque;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px rgba(255, 228, 196, 0.719);
        width: 22%;
        gap: 2rem;
        height: 202px;
        padding-top: 30px;
        padding-bottom: 30px;
      }
      @keyframes move {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
          top: 200px;
          box-shadow: 3px 3px 20px rgba(255, 228, 196, 0.719);
          transform:scale(0.9);

        }
        20% {
          box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px green;
        }
        40%{
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px rgb(175, 209, 175);
        }
        50%{
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px lightgreen;
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
          top: 105px;
          box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px rgba(255, 228, 196, 0.719);
          transform:scale(1);
        }
    }
      .d211 {
        border: 3px 4px 10px ghostwhite;
        box-shadow: 4px 3px 10px rgb(202, 202, 202);
        background-image: url("https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2026/04/06/11/46/11-46-27-808_1280.png");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        width: 60%;
        border-radius: 50%;
        height: 500px;
        transition: 0.2s all ease;
      }
      .d211:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1) translate(5px, -10px);
      }
      .d212 {
        padding-top: 3px;
        text-align: center;
        border: 3px solid bisque;
        border-radius: 10px;

        box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px rgba(255, 228, 196, 0.719);
        width: 80%;
        height: 100px;
        transition: 0.2s all linear;
      }
      .d212 h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .d212:hover {
        background-color: black;
        border-color: whitesmoke;
        box-shadow: 2px 3px 10px grey;
        transform: scale(1.1) translateY(-5px);
      }
      .d212:hover h4 {
        color: white;
      }

      .d22 {
        position: absolute;
        left: 280px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 2ch;
        background-color: bisque;
        border: 4px solid white;
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px white;
        width: 65%;
        transition: 0.1s all ease;
        animation-name: move;
        animation-duration: 2s;
        animation-iteration-count: 1;
        animation-delay: 1s;
        animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
      }
      .d22 p {
        padding: 1ch;
        word-spacing: 5px;
        font-size: 120%;
      }
      .d22 h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .d22:hover {
        transform: translate(-5px, -5px);
        box-shadow: 6px 4px 8px 5px rgb(134, 134, 134);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="d1">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/home.html">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="service.html">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="jobs.html">Career</a></li>
        <li><a href="Log.html">Sign Up</a></li>
        <li><a href="about.html">About Us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="d2">
      <div class="d21">
        <div class="d211"></div>
        <div class="d212">
          <h4>The Black Fox</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="d22">
        <h2>Fennec Fox</h2>
        <hr width="25%" style="margin: auto" />
        <br />
        <p>
          The fennec fox (Vulpes zerda) is a small fox native to the deserts of
          North Africa, ranging from Western Sahara and Mauritania to the Sinai
          Peninsula. Its most distinctive feature is its unusually large ears,
          which serve to dissipate heat and listen for underground prey. The
          fennec is the smallest fox species. Its coat, ears, and kidney
          functions have adapted to the desert environment with high
          temperatures and little water.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
